 125:../../Middlewares/LVGL/GUI/lvgl/src/draw/lv_image_decoder.c ****      * We assume that if a decoder can get the info, it can open the image.
 126:../../Middlewares/LVGL/GUI/lvgl/src/draw/lv_image_decoder.c ****      * If decoder open failed, free the source and return error.
